{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]In 1814 we took a little [F]trip
[G7]Along with Col. Jackson down the mighty [C]mississip'
[F]We took a little bacon and we took a little beans
[G7]And we caught the bloody British in a town in New [C]Orleans
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
